description: Anouk finds herself locked away in Ar's dungeon, handcuffed to the wall. When the handler arrives, he unlocks her from her metal constraints and takes her down to the dungeon floor. There he quickly immobilizes her with a tapegag, and rope bondage - leaving her bound and completely helpless for his future sadistic fantasties!
title: Anouk Immobilized, Mouth-Stuffed, Tapegagged, and Hogtied Up!
